# Bio

PhD Candidate in the Department of Natural Resources and Environmental Management (NREM) at University of Hawai'i (Manoa). Working on Natural Capital Accounting (NCA) and ecosystem valuation projects in the State of Hawai'i. Principal Investigator: Dr Kirsten Oleson.

### Interests

🌱 Ecological Economist \| 🤓 Data Nerd

I am attempting to humanise Economics for the environment and people

